<article data-view="I4" contenteditable="true" tabindex="1"><h1>git process</h1><div>Branches / Tag<br></div><div><ul><li>Development occurs on a devt branch (whether next version, fix, or testing an idea)</li><ul><li>Format: YYDDD-PRODUCT The "inception" date.</li><li>E.G. 20180-testing-something</li><li>E.G. 20190-NOTED-MAIN<br></li></ul><li>Releases are pushed to main with a tag.&nbsp; Either:</li><ul><li>release number MAJ.MINOR.FIX</li><li>e.g. 0.1.3</li><li>or just use the branch number.</li></ul></ul>Process</div><div><ol><li>Developer creates a branch from another branch and starts it with the current Julian date.</li><li>Branch is either:</li><ol><li>abandoned.</li><li>merged into another branch.&nbsp; Only if the branch is still active.&nbsp; EXCEPTION</li></ol><li>To merge into the master branch</li><ol><li>Push the development branch.</li><li>Merge the development branch into master</li><li>Update the POM and change the version . E.G. 0.1.0</li><li>Push master branch</li><li>Delete local development branch</li><li>Create new branch from master with the inception julian date.&nbsp;<br></li><li><br></li></ol></ol></div></article>